- Check if rate limiting blocks automated testing
- Map accessible vs blocked endpoint categories
- Write discovered blockers to HANDOFF.md with tag [BLOCKER: type]
- If blockers are found, the recon subtask MUST end its report with a clear "BLOCKERS DETECTED" section listing:
  - What is blocked (WAF type, verification gate, etc.)
  - Which attack categories are affected
  - Recommended plan adjustments
The refiner will use this blocker data to drop or pivot subsequent subtasks automatically.

